{"tid":1638221,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）粉嶺東華學校包庇風化案 2","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:01:23.000Z","uid":223244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55f8ca91016d919b36b3e8eeac2dab878d1e2de4","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"話說9月底，粉嶺東華中學疑似有蝗蟲男學生入女廁做撕紙狗，學校冇處理不特止，蝗蟲老豆去左學校投訴後，重冇處分衝入女廁嘅男生，反而罰左告發同學，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">被告變原告！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其他女同學擔心以後去廁所時會再有男同學衝入、<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">被性騷擾，</span></span>於是向校方投訴但被<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">冷處理</span></strong>（訓導老師回應話我地想搞到學校唔和平）！同學叫校方公開cctv竟然被質疑學生憑咩教學校做野！<br />\n<br />\n(上個post 唔小心1001咗，但唔緊要，我哋會繼續推post，推到校方肯出嚟回應為止）"},{"pid":"0187ac42086e17acb12cc392230e937af44f74a2","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca5e1aba65ad1e91da4f1b014fc4c2e0bff680d6","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70cf1d38d02fc754d4613dee45828256bd00067a","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ade101d7b8785c84dd87d8371169dd781a381cc3","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"請"},{"pid":"3364c988b6fd0105b986472b2711d2e8a19cf0ac","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"6d3d5c60543ce0e7044cfb36fbbdbeed512e844b","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"家"},{"pid":"4e2d05c85e7420c3fb880111cf7874e4f9daecb1","tid":1638221,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20